title: 4: Nothing To See Here
itunes:title: Nothing To See Here
description: The Readheads Book Club is coming to you live from quarantine. We are recapping this month's book, which was Nothing To See Here by Kevin Wilson. Spoiler alert: Almost all of the girls loved it. They're talking about the major themes in the book, which characters they related to, and who should play each character in a Hollywood adaption of the book. Next month's book is Margo's choice and she chose Before We Were Strangers by Renee Carlino Follow @thereadheads on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/thereadheads/ Join our Facebook group: https://www.facebook.com/groups/thereadheads/ Submit a question or comment to us at thereadheadsbookclub@gmail.com The overall Readheads Rating for Nothing To See Here is 4.15 stars.
